PRF ( PHP - Rails framework )
--------------

PRF is an open source "port" of Ruby on Rails to PHP.
Goal of this project is to help developers build their web applications in a MVC pattern, which lets developers write less code.


Features
-----------
- Database backend ( currently only Mysql, but will feature Postgresql and others in the future )
- MVC ( only model now )

In near future:
- Relationships between models
- Tests
- Caching
- Views / Templates
- Validations
- Generators

Notice
--------------
This is a alpha ( preview ) release of PRF. It isn't stable for production yet!
If you feel contributing in this project, contact me ( Matija Folnovic ) on mail below. Thank you!

